data.description: This cozy well maintained RANCH is tucked away on 1 acre in a peaceful neighborhood. If you are looking for space for your family and to entertain this is the home for you! Features 3 nice size bedrooms, 2 full bath. spacious bonus room, full unfinished basement(stubbed for bath) Nice size kitchen with eat-in area, hardwood floors, beautiful fireplace, huge backyard for great gatherings. Great location!
